  .container
    .jumbotron.text-center
      .logo
        a(href="https://sas.utmn.ru")
          img(src="../assets/Logo__red.png")
      h1 Research Trip Request Form
      form(action="/polls/faculty-research-trips" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data" )
        fieldset
          div(class="input-group")
            .flex-container.column
              label(for="Name") Full Name:
                sup(style="color:red") *
              input(type="text" required="required" class="form-control" name="Name")
            .flex-container.column
              label(for="Country") Country:
                sup(style="color:red") *
                p.small Where a conference/fieldwork will take place.
              input(type="text" required="required" class="form-control" name="Country")
            .flex-container.column
              label(for="City") City:
                sup(style="color:red") *
                p.small Where a conference/fieldwork will take place.
              input(type="text" required="required" class="form-control" name="City")
            .flex-container.column
              label(for="Organization") Organization:
                sup(style="color:red") *
                p.small Which is inviting you.
              input(type="text" required="required" class="form-control" name="Organization")
            .flex-container.column
              label(for="Invitation") Invitation:
                p.small You can upload the program of a conference in case you are acknowledged as a participant in it.
              input(type="file" class="form-control" name="Invitation")
            .flex-container.column
              label(for="Departure date") Departure Date:
                sup(style="color:red") *
                p.small Note that it is the date when you leave Tyumen (or another city if you are not in Tyumen when your research trip/fieldwork starts).
              input(type="date" required="required" class="form-control" name="Departure date")
              label(for="Return date") Return Date:
                sup(style="color:red") *
                p.small Note that it is the date when you arrive in Tyumen (or another city where your research trip/fieldwork ends). Please have a careful look to the second date in your itinerary. It may be so that your flight starts in the evening of one day but ends in the morning of already another day.
              input(type="date" required="required" class="form-control" name="Return date")
            .flex-container.column
              label(for="Need Statement") Need Statement:
                sup(style="color:red") *
                p.small Why is it necessary to go on this research trip/fieldwork?
              input(type="text" required="required" class="form-control" name="Need Statement")
            .flex-container.column
              label(for="Cost Estimates") Cost Estimates:
                sup(style="color:red") *
              input(type="text" required="required" class="form-control" name="Cost Estimates")
            .flex-container.row
              input.form-check-input(type="checkbox" name="Do You Need To Get Money In Advance?")
              label.form-check-label(for="Do you need to get money in advance?") Do you need to get money in advance? 
